headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Nucor Stock Falls as US, Mexico Negotiate on Steel Tariffs
summary: The S&P 500 slipped 0.3% on Wednesday, June 11, as investors weighed softer-than-expected inflation data and progress on U.S.-China trade talks.

headline: Nucor Remembers Dave Aycock, Former CEO and Chairman
summary: The Nucor Corporation (NYSE: NUE) family mourns the loss of former CEO and Chairman Dave Aycock, who passed away on Saturday, June 7, at the age of 94. Aycock, along with Ken Iverson and Sam Siegel, led Nucor's transformation into one of the world's leading steelmakers.
